MongoDB performance test utilities

Prepare MongoDB with test data
1) Start mongod
2) Run "mongo pet" from mongopet folder
3) load("testdata.js")
4) Check that the data is there with db.testdata.find()

Run mongopet test(s)
1) Install sbt
2) Start sbt and run "run"

In case of problems check:
* scala version (tested with 2.9.1)
* sbt version (0.11.2)
* MongoDb host (localhost) and port (27017)
